originalText.text:
I am so thankful that we have a place in the city to come and pray and gather together to learn more about the Word of God. Our church is based in Paramus, but having a place to gather while at university is a blessing. If you want to know who Jesus is, who God is, what Christian faith means, and what the church is meant to be then come to our Mission Center! We have bible study groups during the weekdays and it's a great opportunity for anyone wanting to know more about God whether you are Christian or not, we welcome anyone that is wanting to learn! :)
We also have members that can translate in Spanish(T,W,R), Korean(W), Mandarin(T,R), or Tagalog(T)!
